  <chapter xml:id="Changes-0001">
      <title>Summary of Changes</title>
      <para> The Rackspace Group Admin Extension (&ALIAS;) allows an
            authentication call to return additional information about
            a user's group memberships. </para>
      <section xml:id="NewHeaders-0001">
