      <section xml:id="NewElements-0001">
          <title>New Elements</title>
          <section xml:id="group-0002">
              <title>group</title>
              <para> The &ALIAS; extension returns information about
                    a user's groups as a part of the response when an
                    authentication call is made. Examples of the new
                    elements that are defined as a part of this
                    extension are shown below. </para>
               <example>
                  <title>Groups Response: XML</title>
